# Veritabanı Kuralları (PostgreSQL)

## UUID Primary Key (Zorunlu)

```python
# ❌ YANLIŞ - Integer ID
id = Column(Integer, primary_key=True, autoincrement=True)

# ✅ DOĞRU - UUID
from sqlalchemy.dialects.postgresql import UUID
import uuid

id = Column(UUID(as_uuid=True), primary_key=True, default=uuid.uuid4)
```

## Timestamp Alanları (Her Tabloda)

```python
from sqlalchemy import func

created_at = Column(DateTime(timezone=True), server_default=func.now())
updated_at = Column(DateTime(timezone=True), server_default=func.now(), onupdate=func.now())
```

## Index Kuralları

```python
# Status bazlı sorgular için
__table_args__ = (
    Index('idx_orders_status', 'status'),
    Index('idx_orders_user', 'user_id'),
    Index('idx_kvkk_cleanup', 'photo_deletion_scheduled_at', 
          postgresql_where=text("photo_deletion_scheduled_at IS NOT NULL")),
)
```

## Enum Kullanımı

```python
# ❌ YANLIŞ - String literal
status = Column(String(50))

# ✅ DOĞRU - Python Enum
class OrderStatus(str, Enum):
    DRAFT = "DRAFT"
    TEXT_APPROVED = "TEXT_APPROVED"
    COVER_APPROVED = "COVER_APPROVED"
    # ...

status = Column(SQLEnum(OrderStatus), default=OrderStatus.DRAFT)
```

## Foreign Key İlişkileri

```python
# Cascade delete dikkatli kullan
user_id = Column(UUID(as_uuid=True), ForeignKey('users.id', ondelete='SET NULL'))
product_id = Column(UUID(as_uuid=True), ForeignKey('products.id'), nullable=False)
```

## Migration Kuralları

```bash
# Yeni migration oluştur
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "add_products_table"

# Migration uygula
alembic upgrade head

# Rollback
alembic downgrade -1
```

## ASLA Hard-Code Boyut Kullanma

```python
# ❌ YANLIŞ
width_px = 2480  # Sabit değer

# ✅ DOĞRU - products tablosundan al
product = await get_product(order.product_id)
width_px = mm_to_px(product.width_mm, product.bleed_mm)
```
